  <note>
    <title>Kanban Configuratie 2013</title>
    <created>20121102T014414Z</created>
    <updated>20121102T024115Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space;">
Greenhopper en Jira gebruiken
<div><br/></div><div>Ook kijken naar Trello: <a href="https://trello.com/landing">https://trello.com/landing</a></div><div><br/></div><div><br/><div><br/></div><div>Stappen voor Greenhopper Kanban:</div><div><ul><li>Triage</li><li>Lead</li><li>Grooming</li><li>Awaiting Approval</li><li>Backlog</li><li>In Progress</li><li>QA</li><li>In Limbo</li><li>Done</li></ul><div><br/></div></div></div><div>Swimlanes</div><div><ul><li>Everything else</li><li>Expedite</li><li>Hair on fire</li></ul></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
